new Dean of the divinity school
into jail as a public enemy.

61
00:04:11,952 --> 00:04:16,021
Oh, well, that was
because of the picture
on the bulletin board...

62
00:04:16,023 --> 00:04:18,457
<i>In the</i>
<i>post office.</i>
- Yeah.

63
00:04:18,459 --> 00:04:20,926
