I haven't switched it on yet.

69
00:04:54,395 --> 00:04:57,396
Maybe we better take it
out to the launching site.

70
00:04:57,398 --> 00:04:59,564
Yeah, hurry!

71
00:05:03,737 --> 00:05:06,004
Never mind.
It's too late!

72
00:05:06,006 --> 00:05:09,341
