Ah, chiffon.
J'adore tes yeux bruns,
mon petit chou...

120
00:09:19,259 --> 00:09:22,561
<i>Tu es chou
toi maintenant.</i>

121
00:09:22,563 --> 00:09:24,563
Wha...
What's she sayin'?

122
00:09:24,565 --> 00:09:27,666
Ne pense pas a te sauver,

123
