571
00:46:36,060 --> 00:46:41,130
Of course, I'm not as
sophisticated as she is,

572
00:46:41,132 --> 00:46:45,168
but there is something
about you lately,
something unusual.

573
00:46:51,042 --> 00:46:53,543
You girls know
one another.
- Of course.

574
00:46:53,545 --> 00:46:55,545
