- Hi, franceska.

575
00:46:55,547 --> 00:46:58,247
You both better
ride in front with me.

576
00:46:58,249 --> 00:47:03,019
The wind in the back
is murder on the hair.
You're so thoughtful, buzz.

577
00:47:03,021 --> 00:47:05,521
Et tres charmante,
n'est-ce pas?

578
00:47:05,523 --> 00:47:10,393
Sorry, I don't
speak French.
- Oh.

